title: Alan Moore Collection VI- Made For Moore
description:
So this is me breaking apart my Massive 29 gig Alan Moore Collection into much easier to to download pieces.

This torrent is only a bit under 1 gig and has all the comics that have Alan Moore's name on them but he technically didn't write. Alan Moore either wrote a poem or a movie script and then someone else turned them into comics. 

Titles include Alan Moore's Fashion Beasts, Alan Moore's Hypothetical Lizard, Alan Moore's The Courtyard, Alan Moore's Another Suburban Romance, Alan Moore's Light Of Thy Countenance, Alan Moore's Magic Words, Alan Moore's Old Gansters Never Die

Please enjoy. Please please please donate to this Kickstarter
